spec: the build artefacts in the local maven repository are built as com.github.incept5.correlation.unspecified instead of com.github.incept5.correlation.1.0.0-SNAPSHOT
commitMessage:
Fix Maven artifact versioning in local and JitPack builds

1. Updated build.gradle.kts to always set a default version (1.0.0-SNAPSHOT)
2. Modified the version handling logic to ensure it's never "unspecified"
3. Updated jitpack.yml to handle version extraction more robustly
4. Enhanced CircleCI config to verify local artifacts before triggering JitPack
